{"tid":1619944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老實講我真係好多謝林鄭個仆街","createTime":"2019-10-04T09:01:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T19:41:18.000Z","uid":114186,"like":1443,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"e082d73219228e52ccffd7083b64e32d481b3be8","tid":1619944,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:01:54.000Z","msg":"呢排病左又好攰 人既惰性使然 近幾次都無出 <br />\n以前出黎明明就算得自己一個 都感到好安心<br />\n因為出得黎都係同路人 大家守望相助 互相扶持<br />\n就算自己一個係煲底訓都好有安全感<br />\n落雨有人會遮埋我 警蛆扔tg大家會一齊跑 <br />\n完全唔覺得孤獨！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本身懶到就黎熄左當初肯行出黎示威嗰團火<br />\n覺得都咁多人出 多一個唔多 少一個唔少<br />\n但係今日 多謝呢個垃圾政府 又挑起返我團火<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各位手足 今晚見！不受傷 不流血 不被捕<br />\n香港人加油！<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2425844ebfe91b529153c45fb3ce6bda1b261fe2","tid":1619944,"uid":114186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07ec054eea9990f41430bfee235378da8ed053f","tid":1619944,"uid":114186,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:05:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>今日再次見證左呢個政權的無恥！<br />\n一定會有人絕望到想死!<br />\n唔值得！唔好再諗死！大家一齊捱落去！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"cc7e89846bce0dfdc8f9c21b32cf3c2502066931","tid":1619944,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320e1fd4248e852839485472c72aae31074805e4","tid":1619944,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:09:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ffcbe346dc151